			<br/>
			A Whetstone or Knife Mackaral<span class="mh1"> normally</span> restore 150 hits, and a Mini-Whetstone 100 hits.<span class="mh1"> Sharpness Restoration +25% increases these to 187 and 125 respectively, +50% increases to 225 and 150.</span><br/>
