				<tr>
					<th>Slow</th>
					<td>8 - 10</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody>
		</table>
		<p>
			A bowgun can have one of five different reload speeds, which reduce an ammunition's reload time by the following amounts:
		</p>
		<table>
			<tbody>
				<tr>
					<th>Very Slow</th>
					<td>0</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
