				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th>Very Fast</th>
					<td>4</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody>
		</table>
		<p>
			Reload Speed armor skills can reduce reload even further: each level reduces reload time by one point.
		</p>
		<pre>
			Shot Reload Time - Bowgun Reload - Reload Skill Level
		</pre>

		<h3>Recoil</h3>
		<p>
			<span class="mh1">Recoil is determined entirely by ammunition, and has three possible levels.</span>
			<span class="mhg">Much like Reload Time, Recoil is determined by ammunition, bowgun recoil compensation, and the Recoil armor skill. Nearly all bowguns have "Moderate" recoil compensation (-2 to shot recoil), and a few have "Light" (-3 to shot recoil.)</span>
		</p>
