			Shot Recoil - Bowgun Recoil Compensation - Recoil Skill Level
		</pre>
		<p class="mhg">
			The Rapid Fire skill removes Bowgun Recoil Compensation from the calculation, thus increasing recoil for all shots.
		</p>

		<h3>Critical Range</h3>
		<p>
			Normal and Pierce Shots deal different damage based on how far the shot has to travel to hit the monster. The range during which they deal maximum damage (1.5&times;) is Critical Range. Normal Shot starts in critical range and falls off over time. Pierce Shot starts at 1.0 &times; damage initially, enters Critical Range after a short travel time, and falls off after that. Higher levels of Normal and Pierce Shot remain in their critical range for longer.
