		<h2>Damage to Monsters</h2>

		<h3>Defense Modifier</h3>
		<p>
			A weapon's attack is further modified by the monster's Defense Modifier. This is determined<span class="mh1"> by the monster's category and in which rank it is hunted. See the <a href="/bestiary">Bestiary</a> for which monsters use which Defense Modifiers.</span><span class="mhg"> per monster per quest. See the <a href="/bestiary">Bestiary</a> for the full range of possible Defense modifiers for each monster. See the <a href="/quests">Quests page</a> for the full range of possible Defense Modifiers the monsters on a given quest can have.</span>
		</p>
